features: 【Thickened & Soft】 The gel seat cushion for long sitting size is 43 x 37x 3.5 cm( 16.9 x 14.5 x 1.4 inch), weight about 1kg. Let your hard seat become a softer and more comfortable gel chair cushion.The right thickness can help relieve the pressure of the chair on your body. Make your seat softer and more comfortable with a gel chair cushion.

【Breathability and heat dissipation】 Our gel seat cushion is designed according to the principle of airflow. The double-layered honeycomb structure consists of multiple ventilation holes for excellent breathability and heat dissipation. Compared with Memory Foam cushion, the gel cushion for wheelchair can better reduce sweaty buttocks and keep breathable and not stuffy. The sitting sensation is cooler and more comfortable.

【Relieve Pressure & Pain】 The Gel Wheelchair Cushion is ergonomically designed to evenly distribute the pressure of your body weight, creating multiple points of stress and improving blood circulation to the lower extremities to a greater extent, and effectively relieve lower back, sciatic nerve, tailbone pain relief, coccyx, butt and hip pain. It is a healthy and comfortable gel seat cushion for who sit for a long time.

【Zipper design, easy to clean】The zipper design and removable cloth cover allow for better cleaning of the gel cushion. Our gel cushion is delivered with two machine washable covers! You don't have to worry about getting dirty and not having a replacement available. The black non-slip cover has non-slip bumps on the surface to relieve hip pain and prevent slipping when using the gel cushion.

【Enjoy the Coolness】The Gel seat cushion with cushioning properties is perfect for office chairs, dining chairs, car seats, picnics, wheelchair use, and even sitting still on the floor, no matter stretching or squeezing, it can recover its original shape, very durable. Gel cushions with cooling comfort are perfect as gifts for health-conscious family, friends and coworkers.

reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I really like this cushion by Youngetic. This gel cushion is a nice addition to my firm work chair that I have to sit in each day. It's helped reduce discomfort in my hips and low back in the short week that I've used it at work. My boss and coworkers are looking to buy their own now.
